title: Rosetta's Kitchen
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, American, International, Organic, Take-out, Catering
description: Vegetarian whole food restaurant offerings ethnic, down home cooking using fresh produce from local farms. Menu items such as peanut butter tofu, smashed taters, nutritional yeast gravy, and vegan desserts. Dine in the all hand-crafted wooden furnishing interior, or on an enclosed balcony. Open until late.
